des:
Tadiran IOT products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your air conditioner.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your air conditioner - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your Tadiran IOT products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our " Tadiran IOT " app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one tuya account in our " Tadiran IOT " app;
(3). You need to have some Tadiran IOT devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our " Tadiran IOT " app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in " Tadiran IOT " skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search " Tadiran IOT " skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of " Tadiran IOT ", and you'll be navigated to App name login page;
(9). Input your Replace your App name account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa,turn on the bedroom air conditioner.”
“Alexa,turn off the bedroom air conditioner.”
